  "detailed_description": "<strong>Mike is in trouble! </strong>His garden is growing out of control and needs your help. Match species, use tools creatively and chain incredible combos to survive as long as you can!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/500d182dd21a11c74a6982ddb03c641a.poster.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/500d182dd21a11c74a6982ddb03c641a.webm?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/e54a6f4f171a8488e9479a6df7222c7d.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=91 /></span><br>Make your game unique! Earn seeds each game to unlock new species in your own private Greenhouse.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/b05e8cf03cf10fc1877f9580e9970720.webp?t=1711112486\" width=132 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/e6cb2cd4ac85b87f35d0c99992eb4546.poster.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/e6cb2cd4ac85b87f35d0c99992eb4546.webm?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/8aec72cb1e4b31044399b795c9998945.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=91 /></span><br>Unlock different common, or crazy, garden management tools to keep control of your board.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/b05e8cf03cf10fc1877f9580e9970720.webp?t=1711112486\" width=132 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/f49aa43fbe8bac23f97d1e6943e290c8.poster.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/f49aa43fbe8bac23f97d1e6943e290c8.webm?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/a44046e6a7d2109828d3319f8af10971.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=91 /></span><br>The only way to win is to become the King of the Garden in the Garden of Fame. Beat your friends by mastering your strategy and never sharing your gardening tips and tricks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/b05e8cf03cf10fc1877f9580e9970720.webp?t=1711112486\" width=132 height=20 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/579980f72a17e43f03e29bedfbaa5722.poster.avif?t=1711112486\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/579980f72a17e43f03e29bedfbaa5722.webm?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352420/extras/579980f72a17e43f03e29bedfbaa5722.mp4?t=1711112486\" type=\"video/mp4